	<p>My mother once half-joking/half-serious suggested that just as there is a minimum wage, there should be a maximum wage.  The figure she picked out of the air was $1,000,000.00 a year.  No one can make more than that each year.  Everything beyond that is taxed at 100%.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
