	<p><blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Originally Posted by <b>Tevyn</b><br /><i>Typical response by anybody who is disgruntled about their lot in life. "This sucks and should change. So I'm going to advocate and push for change even though I don't know what to change it to, so let's tear down our existing system without a plan in place for what to replace it with."<br />
