<br />
Improvement is ALWAYS possible.<br />
<br />
And as a nit picky side point, at NO TIME has Taly (or anyone else advocating change) said let's scrap the whole system on a whim.  What we've said is this isn't working as well as it should, let's try and come up with some better ideas.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
